OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPM expected to back loans  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor gas price-hit firms    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Department for Business expects to 
OL,6, get Prime Minister Boris Johnson's     
OL,7, backing for a package to help          
OL,8, energy-intensive industries as gas     
OL,9, prices soar, the BBC understands.      
OL,11,FOn Monday, Business Secretary Kwasi    
OL,12,FKwarteng asked the Treasury to support 
OL,13,Ffirms hit by rising energy costs.      
OL,15,FThe proposals could involve loans worth
OL,16,Fhundreds of millions of pounds.        
OL,18,FThe Treasury is said to be still       
OL,19,Fanalysing the proposal, while Number 10
OL,20,Fhas declined to comment.               
